config BR2_PACKAGE_PAL_OSAL
	bool "Abstraction Layers"
	default y
	help
	  Kernel modules and tools for the abstraction layers. They
	  are used by almost all the scripts and packages for
	  comminucating with the platform and OS.

	  Abstraction Layers
	  ==================
	  osal - Operating System Abstraction Layer - provide os_* symbols
	  pal - Platform Abstraction Layer - provides pal_* symbols

	  Files tagged:
	  $((find -name '*osal*'; find -name '*pal*'; find -name 'get_*') | sort -u)

	  Most people should answer Y.

